Subject: perf test: Additional pipe tests with pipe output written to a file
Git-commit: ccb9004656e55ea13e11e93862aa32aa575bf802
Patch-mainline: v6.12-rc1
References: perf-sp7-v6.12-userspace-update

Additional pipe tests where piped files are written to disk. This
means that spotting a file name of "-" isn't a sufficient "is pipe?"
test.

